Insider Activity


Individual




Kathy N. Waller



Ms. Kathy N. Waller is CFO, President-Enabling Services & Executive VP at The Coca-Cola Co., Chairman at Women’s Leadership Council, Chief Executive & Financial Officer at Energy Brands, Inc. and President & Chief Executive Officer at Jugos del Valle USA, Inc. She is on the Board of Directors at Delta Air Lines, Inc., Monster Beverage 1990 Corp., Monster Beverage Corp., Spelman College, Monster Energy Co. and University of Rochester. Ms. Waller also served on the board at Coca-Cola FEMSA SAB de CV. She received her undergraduate degree from the University of Rochester and an MBA from the University of Rochester.



